name: Cassi with a Cupcake - Cuddli DiDi Doll
description:
Cassi is the cutest member from the Cuddli branch of the DiDi Doll family tree. 
She is hand stitched from red felt printed with tiny white hearts and she has a scrummy pink cupcake appliqued on her body. She has an appliqued and stitched face with brown felt hair.
Cassi has a tiny pocket on her back stitched with the words ‘DiDi Doll’ containing a slip of paper with her name and date. 
She is approx. 5” tall and plumply stuffed with Polyfill.
Cassi is looking for a loving home. (As with all my DiDi Dolls, she is not suitable for young children.)

description:
Priscilla is an ever so sweet member from the Piggi branch of the DiDi Doll family tree.

Priscilla has a tiny pocket on her back stitched with the words ‘DiDi Doll’ containing a slip of paper with her name and date.

Priscilla is looking for a loving home. (As with all my DiDi Dolls, she is not suitable for young children.)

name: Baby JoJo - Babi DiDi Doll
description:
